steps.name: User should give valid username and valid password and enter login button
User should be in valid Search Hotel Page
User should select the location,Hotels, Room Type,No of rooms,Check in date,Check out date,Adults per room, Children per room, from the drop down and click search button
User should be in valid select hotel page
User should select the radio button and then click continue button for the selected Hotel
User should be in valid Book a Hotel page
User should enter first name, last name,billing address,Sixteen digits credit card number,credit card type,the Expiry month and year,valid cvv number, and click the book now button
User should be in valid Booking confimation page
